alwaysApply: false
description: "Comprehensive audit of the entire rules system (specialists, modifiers, contexts, workflows) for health, redundancy, and improvement opportunities"
ide_compatibility: "⚠️ EXTENDED ANALYSIS - Multi-phase audit workflow with substantial output. Use @context-workflow-progress-tracker for session management."
